# Webapp i18n

- Do not add new user-facing hardcoded strings in webapp components.
- Use `formatMessage` / `FormattedMessage` with `id: 'solidtime.*'` and English `defaultMessage`.
- After adding strings, run `make i18n-extract` and update `webapp/src/i18n/ru.json`.
- API errors: map by `code` in `api/errors.ts`; do not show raw server `message` text.
- Plain-string Mattermost APIs (channel header tooltip): use `translate()` from `i18n/helpers.ts` and add keys to both JSON catalogs manually.
